{"tid":334381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【AIR RACE飛行大賽】香港機師蔣霆俄羅斯站歷史性封王!!!","createTime":"2017-07-24T15:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T04:14:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47ef3a824ccb74aec6ba25768d8f09bd305bb20e","tid":334381,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"香港機師蔣霆（Kenny Chiang）周日（23日）在俄羅斯喀山舉行Red Bull Air Race World Championship飛行大賽第5站的挑戰組賽事封王，成為首位香港機師贏得此項賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2_LSL5C_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2_LSL5C_1200x0.PNG&h=5f9603c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首次參賽的蔣霆在較早前的阿聯酋及日本賽站輪空，俄羅斯的賽站是他第3次正式上陣。他以1分07秒264贏得冠軍，時間比次名的法國機師維納（Basptiste Vignes） 及第3名的美國機師高文（Kevin Coleman） 分別快了1秒001及1秒701。蔣霆在俄羅斯站排首名出賽，之後要等待其餘5位機師逐一完成賽事，才能確定冠軍誰屬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn3.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/images/methode/2017/07/24/644b7772-701c-11e7-9a9a-a7d2083b6658_image_hires_174703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn3.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F644b7772-701c-11e7-9a9a-a7d2083b6658_image_hires_174703.jpg&h=dd96c036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賽後他表示：「贏得分站冠軍感覺實在難以置信，我很驚訝，同時真的很高興。我亦要恭喜維納，令今次賽事有兩個新面孔站上頒獎。」擁有豐富花式飛行及駕駛民航機經驗的他表示：「在Red Bull 飛行大賽經驗真的很重要，而我今天亦有一點運氣，我其實未能做出最完美的圈，我希望可以不斷提升自己的表現，這個冠軍無疑給了我很大的動力。」<br />\n<br />\n經過5站賽事，蔣霆目前在挑戰組積分榜以12分排名第6。他在上一站匈牙利其實已有不錯的成績。他在練習賽曾以1分11秒632的最快時間(包括被罰增加的1秒在內)力壓所有機師，包括2016年挑戰組冠軍、德國的波格。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn4.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/images/methode/2017/07/24/79ed0230-701c-11e7-9a9a-a7d2083b6658_image_hires_174703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn4.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F79ed0230-701c-11e7-9a9a-a7d2083b6658_image_hires_174703.jpg&h=ff13580a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRed Bull Air Race World Championship將於9月2-3日移師葡萄牙波圖舉行第6站比賽，之後賽事將於9月及10月則分別在德國及美國上演。"},{"pid":"661376210dbbde1f85b4740f82e2f43436a4d7f2","tid":334381,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://chiangaero.com/mb/news/photos/1/logo_thinner_preview__blog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchiangaero.com%2Fmb%2Fnews%2Fphotos%2F1%2Flogo_thinner_preview__blog.jpg&h=de40f731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image1.redbull.com/rbx02010/0010/1/1330/665/524/article/lead_image/tc_oc_life_sm_0025crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage1.redbull.com%2Frbx02010%2F0010%2F1%2F1330%2F665%2F524%2Farticle%2Flead_image%2Ftc_oc_life_sm_0025crop.jpg&h=0e114a09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ace5ad675feed2403463e9a524f8e0d4e5911757","tid":334381,"uid":66423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f59b5442e08bbbfc37e1a73b7d059048963a0b","tid":334381,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"真？"},{"pid":"96256e6c488e7a792f9d67d8a1844585ec05ec10","tid":334381,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae01863cf3ba2354b7cc6ddaec29e8d964a74cc6","tid":334381,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"香港人平時邊會理呢啲運動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3eebbc7d7e1227848cfee00cd4acc61d30358e","tid":334381,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0